code: @Override @SuppressWarnings("unchecked") public T reduce(T value1, T value2) throws Exception {     if (isTuple) {         Tuple result = ((Tuple) value1).copy().         return fieldAccessor.set((T) result, adder.add(fieldAccessor.get(value1), fieldAccessor.get(value2))).     } else {         T result = serializer.copy(value1).         return fieldAccessor.set(result, adder.add(fieldAccessor.get(value1), fieldAccessor.get(value2))).     } }
